{"tid":1852552,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［正視聽］港共買嘅口罩全部唔係比市民","createTime":"2020-01-30T13:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T13:12:41.000Z","uid":128430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a763cc14e6314ca0990a986ae128ac4ab355065a","tid":1852552,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"張建宗話政府已多在過去一個月，政府已訂購接近500萬個口罩，由上周開始陸續抵港；醫管局亦已採購1 200萬個口罩，其中200萬已到港，另外1 000萬亦即將抵達。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有人可能以為呢啲口罩同市民有關，其實所有都係比政府部門用。唔係比市民！<br />\n<br />\n所謂全球採購根本同市民無關！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/30/P2020013000643.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202001%2F30%2FP2020013000643.htm&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=52d4508c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/30/P2020013000643.htm</a><br />\n留意果500萬不是在「市面供應」果度講"},{"pid":"8240ff6abda2859da00c285b07d59a98aeecec1c","tid":1852552,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ce714c8214b81c2dc3e1928ec52351dbe1f82a9","tid":1852552,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c270bef01eda557624e572c945b1128a091064c","tid":1852552,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T13:10:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fa87653562720c301d3a9bbea2cdcb6eefb59f5","tid":1852552,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T13:10:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed06e27927891c31c8de48e2a1acf5a4647bbd8d","tid":1852552,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0d98d2db256b481b97554980cfd